---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Base 
  title="iTalki vs Preply vs Cambly: Which is Best for You? (2026)" 
  description="We compared the three giants of online English learning. Find out which platform fits your goals, budget, and schedule."
>
  <Header />
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="mb-12 text-center">
      <span class="text-blue-600 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm">Comparison Guide</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mt-4 mb-6 text-gray-900">iTalki vs Preply vs Cambly: Which is Best for You?</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">We compared the three giants of online English learning. Find out which platform fits your goals, budget, and schedule.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">iTalki</h3>
        <p class="text-green-600 font-bold text-lg mb-4">9.2/10</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 text-sm">The world's largest tutor marketplace. Best for flexibility and niche languages.</p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2 mb-8">
          <li>✅ Pay per lesson</li>
          <li>✅ 30,000+ tutors</li>
          <li>✅ No monthly fees</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/reviews/italki/" class="block text-center bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700">Read Review</a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Preply</h3>
        <p class="text-green-600 font-bold text-lg mb-4">8.5/10</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 text-sm">Structured learning with a subscription model. Best for consistent progress.</p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2 mb-8">
          <li>✅ Subscription based</li>
          <li>✅ Structured plans</li>
          <li>✅ Great search filters</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/reviews/preply/" class="block text-center bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700">Read Review</a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Cambly</h3>
        <p class="text-green-600 font-bold text-lg mb-4">8.0/10</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 text-sm">Instant access to native speakers. Best for conversational practice anytime.</p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2 mb-8">
          <li>✅ Instant lessons</li>
          <li>✅ 100% Native speakers</li>
          <li>✅ Casual environment</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/reviews/cambly/" class="block text-center bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700">Read Review</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-16 mb-6">Pricing Comparison</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Pricing is often the biggest factor for students. Here is how they stack up:</p>
    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-12">
      <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50">
            <th class="p-4 border-b">Feature</th>
            <th class="p-4 border-b">iTalki</th>
            <th class="p-4 border-b">Preply</th>
            <th class="p-4 border-b">Cambly</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="p-4 border-b font-semibold">Min. Price</td>
            <td class="p-4 border-b">$5/hour</td>
            <td class="p-4 border-b">$10/hour</td>
            <td class="p-4 border-b">$15/hour</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="p-4 border-b font-semibold">Payment Type</td>
            <td class="p-4 border-b">Pay per lesson</td>
            <td class="p-4 border-b">Subscription</td>
            <td class="p-4 border-b">Subscription</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="p-4 border-b font-semibold">Trials</td>
            <td class="p-4 border-b">Discounted trials</td>
            <td class="p-4 border-b">100% satisfaction guarantee</td>
            <td class="p-4 border-b">Paid 15-min trial</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-16 mb-6">Which One Should You Choose?</h2>
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Choose iTalki if...</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">You want total control over your spending. iTalki is the only platform here that does not force you into a subscription. It is perfect if you have a busy schedule or a tight budget.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Choose Preply if...</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">You want to build a long-term habit. The subscription model keeps you accountable. Preply is also excellent if you need a tutor for a specific professional goal, like passing the IELTS or preparing for a job interview.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Choose Cambly if...</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">You just want to talk. Cambly is great for learners who are shy and want to practice conversation in a low-pressure environment. You can log in at any time and find a tutor ready to chat.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 bg-blue-50 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-blue-100">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Our Verdict</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 mb-6 leading-relaxed">For most learners, iTalki remains the top choice due to its flexibility and massive selection of tutors. However, if you prefer a structured learning path, Preply is a very close second.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/reviews/italki/" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">Start with iTalki</a>
        <a href="/reviews/preply/" class="bg-white text-blue-600 border border-blue-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors">Compare Preply</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "ItemList",
    "name": "iTalki vs Preply vs Cambly",
    "description": "Comparison of the top three online English tutoring platforms",
    "itemListElement": [
      {
        "@type": "ListItem",
        "position": 1,
        "item": {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "SoftwareApplication",
            "name": "iTalki"
          },
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "9.2"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "ListItem",
        "position": 2,
        "item": {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "SoftwareApplication",
            "name": "Preply"
          },
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "8.5"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "ListItem",
        "position": 3,
        "item": {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "SoftwareApplication",
            "name": "Cambly"
          },
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "8.0"
          }
        }
      }
    ]
  }
  </script>
  <Footer />
</Base>
